          "evidence": "The South Zone dove hunting season structure during the first segment will include an earlier regular season opening date (Sept. 1 – Oct. 25), eliminate the Special White-winged Dove Days, and institute standardized daily bag limits and shooting hours across all days in the South Zone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Duck bag limits have species-specific restrictions: 5 mallards (max 2 hens), 3 wood ducks, 3 pintails, 2 redheads, 2 canvasbacks, 1 scaup, 1 dusky duck (mottled/Mexican/black duck).",
