          "evidence": "Daily bag 6 in aggregate, with no more than: 5 mallards (only 2 of which may be hens), 3 wood ducks, 3 pintails, 2 redheads, 2 canvasbacks, 1 scaup, 1 dusky duck."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Dusky ducks (mottled, Mexican, black duck, and hybrids) are off-limits for the first 5 days of the regular season in each zone.",
